Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:28.83,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}夏！忘記寫作業
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:31.63,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}秋！跑馬拉松最後一名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:33.80,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}冬！長居被爐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:39.38,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一年365天 時而366天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:45.92,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雖然有很多事情 全力！全開！全心全力！享受吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:48.27,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}「Enjoy！Enjoy！Jojojojoy！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:53.82,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}啊～青春！耀眼的青春！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:58.99,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}跟睡意說再見 打開心中的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:04.12,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}啊～青春！全速前進的青春！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:09.42,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不珍惜時光的話 可會錯過許多樂趣唷 注意！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.62,0:23:14.70,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}青春All right 青春Oh yes 謳歌青春 全力以赴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.75,0:23:18.56,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}青春Don't mind 青春Fight 青春最高
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:20.53,ED_TW,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Yeah！！ Yeah！！ Yeah！！ Yeah！！
Comment: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:38.17,YY-main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:36.29,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.57,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,接下來是衣服...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:49.50,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,給京子打電話...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.92,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不 不行 一定會被她捉弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:56.72,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,喂 我是燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.30,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,一大早的不好意思 現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.41,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯 方便
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.35,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那個 燈里...喜歡蜘蛛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:06.38,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:06.38,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,{\an7}日語中蜘蛛和雲的發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:08.57,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,雖然我也覺得妳不太可能喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.27,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.27,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,燈里喜歡雲喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.72,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,欸 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.96,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯 光是看著就感到很溫馨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:16.52,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,又軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:20.33,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,小時候就夢想著能坐到雲的上面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.44,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,欸 真是奇怪的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:26.04,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,的確有點孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.16,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,孩子氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:29.84,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:33.41,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,妳那麼喜歡蜘蛛的話能來我家一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.10,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:42.30,YY-ep-title,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,{\pos(1515,892)}#02 感受恐懼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:38.68,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.34,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,路上小心點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:46.31,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.70,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,趁誰都不在的時候 把這個洗掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.19,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:03.82,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,蜘蛛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:07.21,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,真是的 結衣 妳是為了嚇我一跳才叫我過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:09.32,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,咦 妳不是說妳喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.61,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,不要開這種奇怪的玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:14.75,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那就沒辦法了 雖然可能也指望不上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.88,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,結衣學姊竟然給我打電話 我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.76,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,千夏醬 今天有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.97,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,難道這是在邀請我去約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:24.40,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,有空 有空 有空到都快閒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.91,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那妳能來我家一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:28.21,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,其實...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.05,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,{\a6}我立刻就過去 飛著過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.04,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,我將化身成光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.98,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,請叫我千夏之光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.65,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯...那我等著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.69,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.03,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,千夏醬 今天看起來好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:47.24,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,欸？為什麼又突然沮喪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.91,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:52.15,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,話說回來 結衣學姊 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.12,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,其實我家裡出現了蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:58.88,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,妳也不擅長對付吧 果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.61,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,蜘蛛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.67,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,雖然我很怕 但是能對付它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:03.80,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.22,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,這比我想像的還要大 這我可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.85,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,稍微超出了用紙巾消滅的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.19,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.75,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,但是如果在這時候表現出自己的出色一面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:18.11,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,也許就能抓住結衣學姊的心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.14,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,對啊 如果連蜘蛛都抓不住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:26.20,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,更何談抓住結衣學姊的心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:29.20,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,徒手？沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.43,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.54,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,只要是為了結衣學姊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:44.59,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,糟了 下午學校還有課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:00.86,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.00,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,差點就要輸在社會上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.82,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,這也是對虧了燈里的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.42,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,我知道了 還不快點幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.83,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:16.95,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好 這個杯子和傳單借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:23.67,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,手法真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.46,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,成功討伐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:29.95,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:33.19,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,結衣 妳以前不是不怕蟲的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.34,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,以前是以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.40,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,居然怕蟲子 真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.15,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,真多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.32,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,還特地叫妳們過來 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:46.18,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,難得的機會 今天我們就一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:46.90,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:48.82,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,還要把燈里叫醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.85,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,正好肚子有點餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.08,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那我們要不要做鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.50,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,展現技術的時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:58.30,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,把窗戶關上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:04.51,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,好棒 鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.56,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,好久沒有吃到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.59,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,還有鮮奶油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.05,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.60,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,來 給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.31,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,要快點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.18,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,要我來弄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.55,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,表面不斷在冒小泡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.65,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:24.75,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,喂 完全不起泡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.34,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,就沒有自動攪拌機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:28.92,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,我平時又不怎麼做點心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.71,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,右臂逐漸開始累積疲勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.24,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.23,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,快點弄完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.50,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,要是我的右臂變得都是肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.41,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,妳們還會跟我玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.25,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我來幫妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.01,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,燈里要是都是肌肉 確實有點難接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:47.66,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:48.84,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.00,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,是心形嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.02,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯 勉勉強強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.67,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,完成的話就給妳吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.64,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,可以嗎 學姊的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.29,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,妳那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.52,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,不錯的肌肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.74,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,做好了就送給結衣妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.48,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.96,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,鮮奶油做好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:06.78,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.45,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,這裡還有一盒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.86,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,手會斷掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.28,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,難得的機會 我們做一下裝飾然後交換一下吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:15.83,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,想法不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.60,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,給 正在洗頭的肌肉人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.41,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,都說過我不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.25,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,給 千夏醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.70,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,雖然做的不怎麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:25.79,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.22,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,京子 做好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.13,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,做得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.51,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,這是我的得意之作喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:32.94,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,這是燈里的臉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.16,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,是熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.14,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,妳只是從糰子判斷是我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.13,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,這個給妳 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:40.85,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,完全看不出是薄餅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.09,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,這是我用心做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.11,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,謝...謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:48.36,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,那麼 結衣學姊的心...我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.69,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:51.95,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,京子妳在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:56.77,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,像這樣先畫畫然後再這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.18,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.46,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,京子就對這方面很擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.50,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,有什麼想讓我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.80,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,那麼 能做出小貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:12.80,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.59,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.00,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.43,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,不 雖然是對了 不過還是不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.72,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,燈里妳也試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.39,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:23.85,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,滴這個很難的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.16,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:43.42,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,燈里真喜歡做自己的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.03,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,都說過是熊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.11,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,妳又從糰子來判斷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.09,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,燈里妳真是喜歡熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:54.93,YY-main,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\fn華康秀風體W3\c&H0000&\bord0\b0\frz14\pos(316,134)}最強且又究極之作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:54.93,YY-main,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\fn華康秀風體W3\c&H0000&\bord0\b0\frz14\pos(404,208)}與朗姆葡萄乾冰淇淋的搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.88,YY-main,MOM,0,0,0,,媽媽朋友的女兒買了這件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:03.10,YY-main,MOM,0,0,0,,但是和印象中的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.89,YY-main,MOM,0,0,0,,我想著小綾應該合身 所以就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:08.90,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,但是...這麼可愛的衣服...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.77,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,絕對不適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.23,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:21.42,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,快點做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.00,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.75,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,喂喂 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:29.65,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,要是能再認真一點學習的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.06,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,考試之前就不用那麼慌張了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.70,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,樣子不對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.91,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,發生了什麼令人沮喪的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:41.30,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,難道是因為我偷吃了向日葵的伙食？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.45,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,或者是因為在身體檢查的時候搗蛋的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:44.93,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,或者說還是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.63,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,竟然對著作業那麼認真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.44,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,終於有幹勁了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:53.73,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,櫻子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:54.99,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.17,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,來玩撲克牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.36,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,咦？妳不喜歡玩撲克牌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.49,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,那樣的話 那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:04.20,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,來玩黑鬍子海盜危機一發怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.08,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.11,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,居然還有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:12.39,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,難道她拒絕學習是因為有什麼理由嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:15.05,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,有什麼痛苦的回憶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.16,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:19.01,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,她在苦惱著什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.07,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,櫻子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:24.68,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,妳有什麼苦惱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.39,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,問妳自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.15,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,不 並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.19,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,嘛 畢竟還是櫻子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.05,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會有苦惱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.73,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,妳什麼意思嘛 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.26,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,妳在聽我說話嗎 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.20,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.20,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.71,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,我明明這麼小聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:49.02,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,她這樣過剩反應 難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.08,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,苦惱的原因是胸部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.51,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,之前也有過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.15,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,又成長了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:58.03,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,話說回來 我的到底什麼時候才會成長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.80,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,至少告訴我成長時間啊成長時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.80,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,好像沒什麼精神的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.43,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,真的有那麼討厭學習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:10.03,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,難道認識到自己是笨蛋了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:14.75,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,因為這樣下去無法前進而苦惱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:17.32,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,這裡得狠下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.01,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,櫻子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.26,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.35,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,因為說的是正經話 聽清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.28,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:27.49,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,那個 妳的確是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.27,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,但是沒有必要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:32.62,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,還有 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:37.80,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,我也並不是討厭...笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:41.59,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,不僅被認定為了笨蛋 而且還被鼓勵了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.34,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:44.78,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,不做了不做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.67,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,今天不適合學習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.34,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,欸 妳說什麼....？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.81,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,沒辦法集中精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.09,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,明明應該向日葵教我寫作業的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.44,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,妳一直在想著其他事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.02,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.90,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,我可是一直想著櫻子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.11,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.36,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,妳說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:09.45,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,妳是笨蛋嗎 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:12.44,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,別一下子就叫別人是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.90,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,我才不想被向日葵這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:22.34,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,算了 真是的 快點教我寫作業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.13,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:26.80,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,自己願意學習了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.65,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,咦 一下子又高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.98,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,她到底在為了什麼而苦惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:36.33,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,那櫻子 這裡的答案是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.01,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,胸部...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.11,YY-main,SAKURAKO,0,0,0,,看來並不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:40.89,YY-main,HIMAWARI,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.90,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.35,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,這件衣服真...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.88,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,難得我穿上了 出去散散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:13:00.44,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,這條路沒什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.20,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,咦 這不是綾乃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.55,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,歲...歲納京子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.27,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,妳在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.00,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,從結衣家回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.72,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,還買了漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.74,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,咦？那件衣服是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:13.81,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.82,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,唔 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:18.54,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,這個蝴蝶結是我縫上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:23.22,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,收下這件衣服的原來是綾乃的媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.14,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,真是的 討厭 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.21,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,我去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.52,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:30.23,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,有什麼關係呀 畢竟蠻適合妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.61,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,真的？看起來不奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.10,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,嗯 超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.21,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,正好有空 去那邊公園逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.57,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,真拿妳沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.94,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,就逛一會喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.48,YY-main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.67,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,妳那身衣服也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:51.56,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,歲納京子是想買下這件衣服自己穿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:52.61,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:56.90,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,和漫畫裡的衣服很相似 所以打算在舉辦活動的時候穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.65,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,但是裙子不盡人意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:00.73,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,難道這是cosplay嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.47,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:03.65,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,很適合妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.53,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,超適合塔里木盆地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.50,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,超適合塔里木盆地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:13.26,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,綾乃竟然是那種反應 有點說不過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.50,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.63,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,妳不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.00,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,儘管裝傻倫敦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.27,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,怎麼感覺被人照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.09,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,難道她不是有意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.96,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,話說回來 妳買了什麼漫畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.90,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,米拉庫露的最新作喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.12,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,難不成這就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:35.82,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,對對 我就是想做這身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.31,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,米拉庫露的覺醒模式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.27,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,綾乃平時看漫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.32,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,是啊 稍微看過一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:44.11,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,報紙裡的四格漫畫之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.56,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,那種的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.65,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,偶爾還看少女漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:48.78,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.78,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,米拉庫露也是少女漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.16,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,妳看一下試試吧 我下次借給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:56.03,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,妳真是喜歡那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.71,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,什麼啊 沒必要笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.29,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.50,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.48,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我突然感到口渴了 我去買喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:07.13,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,綾乃要喝什麼？我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.43,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.23,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.74,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,謝謝 那給我檸檬茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.80,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我知道了 紅豆湯是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.26,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,一個字都沒對上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.76,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,逗妳的逗妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.61,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,紅豆湯是吧 我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.48,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,是檸檬茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:34.17,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.78,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,我剛剛才察覺到 這莫非就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.47,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,約...約...約會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.67,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,怎...怎...怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:45.01,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,突然就緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.82,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,要是我沒注意到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.05,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.33,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.91,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,紅豆湯沒賣 幫妳買了檸檬茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.51,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,別總是讓我吐槽妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.89,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,剛才還聊的好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:06.97,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,難得的兩人相處 今天一定要拿出勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:09.17,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.08,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,什...什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.99,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,不 抱歉 不值一提的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.56,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,綾乃妳先說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:20.86,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,歲納京子妳除了漫畫還喜歡什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:25.29,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我想想 我平時只是做我想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.97,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,今天在結衣家裡做了鬆餅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:29.72,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:30.63,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:32.48,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.00,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.77,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,在結衣家裡做的餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:36.96,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,送給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:37.86,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.26,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,大家一起做的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.60,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,我能收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.48,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.73,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:49.52,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,妳剛才想說的是什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.46,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,算了 只是不值一提的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.10,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,這不是讓我更在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.12,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,真的只是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:57.74,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,那朵雲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.95,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,很像是燈里與炸蝦的合體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:03.83,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,真的是不值一提的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.60,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,綾乃妳有喜歡做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.69,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:12.38,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,我喜歡邊泡在水中邊想事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.32,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,泡在水中...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:20.11,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,妳又在想什麼無聊的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.70,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,對了 我還喜歡收集角色周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.13,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,喔！什麼樣的角色？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.79,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,例如海蜇三姊妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.47,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,三連體的那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.27,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,對 對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.12,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,真不知道妳還喜歡那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:36.10,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,因為不好意思啊 不敢拿去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:41.53,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,要是我的話 COS米拉庫露也不會覺得害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.48,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,不 妳倒是給我感到羞恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:48.46,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,糟了 今天要早點回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.95,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,謝謝妳陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.61,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:53.92,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:56.80,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,歲納京子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.84,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,那個...下次...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.52,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.83,YY-main,KOYKO,0,0,0,,下次我們兩個人再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:13.82,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,真拿妳沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.50,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,那件衣服 要好好珍惜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.32,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,嗯 今天謝謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.31,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,有時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:27.52,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,挑戰精神也是很重要的 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.66,YY-main,TOMOKO,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.80,YY-main,TOMOKO,0,0,0,,難道剛才打瞌睡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:35.95,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.56,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,枕套還在外面曬著...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.93,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,得在燈里看到之前收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.44,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,要是被看到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.74,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,這是...什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.35,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,不是這樣的 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.84,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說 這個也太...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:53.31,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,這份愛太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:57.16,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,從今天開始我就去結衣她們那裡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.61,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.28,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,燈里 等一下 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.74,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:10.43,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,光是想像心跳就加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.52,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我最喜歡姊姊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:16.31,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,最喜歡了 最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.61,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,就像魔法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:20.93,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,僅僅是想像一下燈里的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.68,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,心境就能如此平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.86,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,現在不是平靜的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.39,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,那份笑容就快要消失在我面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.55,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,抱歉 智子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:29.89,YY-main,TOMOKO,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.68,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,我今天就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:34.54,YY-main,TOMOKO,0,0,0,,欸？難道妳身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.90,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:43.82,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,要快點把枕套收起來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.14,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,拜託 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:50.60,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,再在結衣家玩一會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.89,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,已經 回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.94,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:06.79,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,課已經上完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.18,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.44,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,那個 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:10.89,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.48,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:15.08,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,{\an8}別靠近我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:17.27,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.65,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,對不起 姊姊真是糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.93,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,不如死掉算了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:23.68,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:27.37,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,被燈里討厭了 被燈里拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.08,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,我已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.56,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.84,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,妳不是說「別靠近我」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:36.15,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,不是的 不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.76,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.25,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.39,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我從朋友那裡學來了做法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:45.44,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,這是...餅乾？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:49.15,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我試著做出來了 想用來感謝我溫柔的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.68,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,雖然結衣她們也幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.39,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我本想先包裝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.69,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,結果姊姊早一步回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:02.56,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,要是不合口味的話 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.14,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,怎麼會不好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:09.96,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,因為是我最心愛的妹妹做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.58,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,姊姊 最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:16.05,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,快吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:17.26,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:21.52,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,不過在這之前妳能先上去二樓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.32,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:28.70,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:31.08,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,簡直就像在店裡買到的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.16,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:33.89,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:36.39,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,咦？只吃一口嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:38.69,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,因為一次吃完太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.43,YY-main,AKANE,0,0,0,,我想一點一點吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.46,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,姊姊妳真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:46.07,YY-main,MOM,0,0,0,,小綾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.12,YY-main,MOM,0,0,0,,妳還不換衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.78,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,再等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:24.36,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:34.04,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,姊姊 妳再怎麼吃也吃得太慢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:38.37,YY-crossreview,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\frz10.27\pos(36,96)}輕鬆百合 評論
